          experiences such as the number of countries or continents visited and will be able to add other
          users as “friends” who will be able to see each other’s profiles.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12">
        <h3 class="feature-title">Travel Advisories</h3>
        <a href="/destinations/advisories"><img src="./image/column3.jpg" class="img-fluid"></a>
        <p>Stay safe and prepared abroad. Know the current risk levels and the entry/exit requirements
          for destinations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

